            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">
                
                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
                </p>
                <p>
                    matirai koṇṭa kōpparakēcarivaṉmakki yāṇṭu <num value="20"><unclear>2 <g type="numeral">10</g></unclear></num> Āvatu
                </p>
                <p>
                    kuṉṟakūṟṟa
                    <lb n="2"/>Avanikaṉtaṟppapurattu <hi rend="grantha">mahade</hi>varkku Ittaḷi kuttapiḷ<unclear>l</unclear>ai kumiḻi tar<unclear>u</unclear>ṇaval
                    <lb n="3"/>li Oru nontāviḷakku <hi rend="grantha">cantrādi</hi>ttaval Eriya vaita poṉ patiṉ ka
                    <lb n="4"/>ḻañcu
                </p>
                <p>
                    Ippoṉ patiṉ kaḻañcum koṇṭōm koṇṭu Oru no
                    <lb n="5"/>ntāviḷakkukku nicatam Uḻakku ney Aṭṭuvōm āṉōm Ava
                    <lb n="6"/>ṉikantavappurattu nakarattōm Ivvaṉ
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <lem>yāṇṭu <unclear>20</unclear></lem>
                        <note>ARE proposes 37th year but I cannot see it. There may be another number after the 20 that I read, but, if there was, it is no longer legible.</note>                        
                    </app>
